Class Coordinates

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.ruleant.getback_gps.lib.Coordinates

  • public class Coordinates
extends Object
    Coordinates is a container that can contain multiple instances of a Coordinate class.

    Dieter Adriaenssens
